<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    /* Simple reset */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #007BFF;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: white !important;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Password Reset</h1>
    <p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>
    <p>You requested a password reset for your account associated with this email: <strong>{{email}}</strong>.</p>
    <p>Your new temporary password is:</p>
    <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #d9534f;">{{password}}</p>

    <p>Please use this password to log in and be sure to change it after you sign in.</p>

    <a href="http://localhost:5173/login" class="button">Log in to your account</a>

    <p>If you did not request this change, please contact our support immediately.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
